{"tid":2109942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食肆今起禁晚市堂食　上夜班市民改到公園食外賣","createTime":"2020-07-15T14:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T14:13:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25609dfcc5a38b4a9518eca1870b483a4ea48144","tid":2109942,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/3f1f64adbb26844cd3dbf15a3a350997/2020/07/089663249e625b37c40506ec6eab36bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F3f1f64adbb26844cd3dbf15a3a350997%2F2020%2F07%2F089663249e625b37c40506ec6eab36bd.jpg&h=fa90589f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n便利店不能叮飯 夜更市民公園吃飯 <br />\n<br />\n在灣仔港灣道花園，有6、7名市民食外賣，有在附近寫字樓返夜更的人說，平日會在附近餐廳堂食，可以涼冷氣，但禁令之下，連便利店都不容許他在店內食「叮飯」，唯有改到公園，未來幾日會提早在下午5時許食晚飯，免卻麻煩。 有在食肆外等外賣的市民說，禁晚上堂食會造成不便；亦有市民說，疫情起大半年已習慣放工後，買外賣回家食，認為新政策對他無影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347238/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2347238%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Guxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=52c28b13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347238/</a>"},{"pid":"783841d934763d8dbcee535b8a9e06b4447ce75b","tid":2109942,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"幾時都話香港人識靈活變通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}